{{Quote|Yes, Cliff Clavin, the Boston letter carrier and know&ndash;it&ndash;all barfly, is in ''The Empire Strikes Back'' &mdash; at least for a couple of scenes and a couple of lines.|[[Jason Fry]]|<ref name="Postman">{{SWArchive|url=episode-v/bts/article/f20011217/index.html|text=John Ratzenberger: The Postman Always Strikes Back}}</ref>}}
'''John Ratzenberger''' is an actor who played [[Major]] [[Bren Derlin]] in [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''The Empire Strikes Back'']]. Soon after, his career exploded with his role as "[[Wikipedia:Cliff Clavin|Cliff Clavin]]" in [[Wikipedia:Cheers|''Cheers'']] and, later, in all of the [[Wikipedia:Pixar|Pixar]] animated movies.

Ratzenberger was thirty-two years old when he portrayed Derlin, spending about a week filming his scenes at [[Elstree Studios]] in a suburb north of [[Wikipedia:London|London]]. Ratzenberger reprised his role as Derlin thirty-seven years later in ''[[LEGO Star Wars: The Freemaker Adventures]]''.

